\lang english
4.
 Compliance and Exceptions
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
Compliance with this policy is mandatory for all Information Operations personnel and County officials exercising authority over or within the Information Operations Department.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Assessment
\series default
:
 Compliance with delegation requirements shall be assessed through the annual policy review and maturity scoring process defined in 
\series bold
Policy 
